org.archive.wayback.archivalurl

Class ArchivalUrlContextResultURIConverterFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.archive.wayback.archivalurl.ArchivalUrlContextResultURIConverterFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ContextResultURIConverterFactory

    public class ArchivalUrlContextResultURIConverterFactory
extends Object
implements ContextResultURIConverterFactory
    ContextResultURIConverterFactory which creates a context specific ArchivalUrlResultURIConverter, given a base ArchivalUrlResultURIConverter and the flags to add.

    Note that this class expects requested resource type flags (ex "cs_" as an argument to getContextConverter(String). This is a very specific usage and It will not be useful other than the context of rewriting resources with specific non-default types of hyper-links (specifically, ArchivalUrlSAXRewriteReplayRenderer, and ArchivalURLJSStringTransformerReplayRenderer).

    It is highly likely this class gets refactored, and may be discontinued as a result.
